{"tid":2144594,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】政府要你飲嘅水同打嘅針 原來係咁得人驚","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T21:40:42.000Z","uid":307619,"like":292,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"34e85a5acd978cc9b3c878cefb0aab7785886471","tid":2144594,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"嗱嗱嗱～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知算唔算呃咗大家入嚟<br />\n我講緊ViuTV嘅電視劇情咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果睇過嘅巴絲請skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"brown\">《理想國：沒有悲傷的世界》</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aXcjrhU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaXcjrhU.png&h=8f0ecd7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5E2o4C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5E2o4C.png&h=0c3d2319&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8qTCcXZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8qTCcXZ.png&h=90a5eecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">劇中所有人都需要被監察飲政府提供嘅玫瑰水<br />\n飲完之後就嗰個人就會變得好快樂</span><br />\n所有殘酷嘅現實都會變得好美好<br />\n一旦唔飲水就會見返現實嘅一面<br />\n然後被追殺 <br />\n逼到你肯飲為止<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"brown\"><span class=\"x-large\">《黑市：偽善若水》</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ffiq6jQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfiq6jQ.png&h=8035d4b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jppqmTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjppqmTf.jpg&h=b765a7af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z0d6QMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0d6QMM.png&h=371a3005&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PLMPOyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPLMPOyt.png&h=e5c682f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"orange\">劇中新型流感蔓延<br />\n市民都要強制去診所打疫苗</span><br />\n打完之後大家都會變得盲目樂觀<br />\n成為一個聽聽話話嘅市民<br />\n邊一個唔肯打亦都會面對生命威脅<br />\n逼到你肯打為止<br />\n（01就唔貼link了）<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n當年《十年》上映<br />\n除咗催淚彈一幕之外<br />\n好多人對其他情節可能冇乜共鳴<br />\n但而家我知道原來《十年》並唔需要十年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWaUfeG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWaUfeG.jpg&h=790dd830&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b08598c0f33eba2b805375d4e25fde6b0deef3c","tid":2144594,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"068e31449652a8a4d9ca9e96c750f914bd52a91f","tid":2144594,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:25:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac1d34d995662f7a49460bc7c60be19892314a08","tid":2144594,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"410afdb6b8e381075475d5542ab6dab5871103ad","tid":2144594,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3359a30442db97ca1ae9941042c7d4f234566ea","tid":2144594,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:27:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c4f1e10dc42f73d53aaade145c560d5c71889cc2","tid":2144594,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:33:17.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dee1db1820d399212f899c10ea28492b03717a","tid":2144594,"uid":147728,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:33:24.000Z","msg":"we happy few<img src=\"/assets/fac